divs: Sighting DetailsI was cleaning the pool on a nice sunny afternoon and noticed that the moon was really bright. I thought it would make a good picture with the moon shining on a sunny day instead of at night. Anyways I grabbed my camera and while it was turning on I could see this shiny object flying across the sky that didn't look like a normal plane, there were no wings, and it made a swishing sound. I got a picture of it and it was gone. I took some more pictures of the moon and later when I downloaded them to my computer, I noticed the object in another picture I took by the moon but it is quite high up and just looks like a spec.
Summary: I took a couple of pictures of an object flying across the sky with no wings.
